  - m_Id: 73607598048272384
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272385
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272386
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272387
    m_Localized: The cathedral stands on one of the oldest parts of Wroclaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272388
    m_Localized: People know it for its tall towers and quiet island streets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272389
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272390
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272391
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272392
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272393
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272394
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272395
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272396
    m_Localized: Market Square is one of the busiest places in Wroclaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272397
    m_Localized: Many people look for dwarf statues there while they walk.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272398
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272399
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272400
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272401
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272402
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272403
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272404
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272405
    m_Localized: The Old Town Hall is one of the most important old buildings in
      the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272406
    m_Localized: It stands in the middle of Market Square.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272407
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272408
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272409
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272410
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272411
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272412
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272413
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272414
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272415
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272416
    m_Localized: Panorama Raclawicka wraps a giant picture around the room.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272417
    m_Localized: It makes history feel big and close.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272418
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272419
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272420
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272421
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272422
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272423
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272424
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272425
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272426
    m_Localized: Wroclaw is famous for its dwarf statues.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272427
    m_Localized: Each dwarf can tell a small story about the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272428
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272429
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272430
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272431
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272432
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272433
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272434
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272435
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272436
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272437
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272438
    m_Localized: Centennial Hall is known for its big round roof.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272439
    m_Localized: It is one of the best known buildings in Wroclaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272440
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272441
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272442
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272443
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272444
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272445
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272446
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272447
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272448
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272449
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272450
    m_Localized: The fountain mixes water, light, and music.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272451
    m_Localized: At night the show can feel like a dance.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272452
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272453
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272454
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272455
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272456
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272457
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272458
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272459
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272460
    m_Localized: Olga Tokarczuk is a Polish writer from this region.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272461
    m_Localized: Her books made her famous in many countries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272462
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272463
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272464
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272465
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272466
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272467
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272468
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272469
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272470
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272471
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272472
    m_Localized: The plaza is an open place next to Sky Tower.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272473
    m_Localized: People pass by, meet friends, and rest there.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272474
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272475
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272476
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272477
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272478
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272479
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272480
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272481
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272482
    m_Localized: Sky Tower is one of the tallest buildings in Wroclaw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272483
    m_Localized: From the top, you can see a large part of the city.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272484
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272485
    m_Localized: 
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73607598048272486
    m_Localized: 
